high_descs: Walk straight and reach the desk on the left side
Take a butter knife from the top of the desk
Turn right and take few steps to reach the drawer
Open the drawer and put the butter knife in it and close the drawer
Turn back and walk towards fridge and reach it
Open the fridge and take a butter knife from it and close the fridge
Turn back and walk towards a drawer
Open the drawer and put the butter knife next to the first knife and close the drawer
anns.task_desc: Put the butter knife in the drawer

high_descs: Turn left to the desk.
Pick the butter knife from the desk.
Turn left to the drawer.
Place the butter knife inside the drawer.
Turn left towards the fridge.
Place the butter knife inside the drawer.
Turn left to the drawer.
Place the butter knife inside the drawer.
anns.task_desc: To place the butter knife inside the drawer.

high_descs: Go straight ahead and stop at the brown desk to the left, before the microwave.
Pick up the butter knife from the desk.
Turn right and head to the drawers just ahead that the microwave is on top of.
Place the knife into the bottom drawer.
Turn around and go straight ahead to the fridge.
Remove the butter knife from the fridge.
Go back to the drawers with the microwave on top.
Place the second butter knife into the bottom drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place two butter knives in a drawer.
